  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I thought maybe I am crazy now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I started thinking in pictures.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I was called to a patient, what-- how was it?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had such a special bag, which doctors have here too, but another one.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I took the bag and I climbed stairs, whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I examined a patient.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And later I sat down and I wrote.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What did I wrote?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the first word came to me, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That time was in style, you know-- A painkiller?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], from Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from-- I had [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I got aspirin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Uh-huh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So my memory probably started working.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I reminded myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wrote cotton, alcohol, iodines, a few-- a bandage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said, that's all?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I couldn't tell her that I don't remember anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I said, for the moment, that's all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't remember, but then I was so smart to tell her, for the moment.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyhow, she let me go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And later, gradually, I became back to earth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I told that I need this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow, she couldn't give me more.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A bandage was from paper.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I rolled on paper.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the girls-- so now we will-- I am already settled.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the girls are going to-- to the factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So five o'clock in the morning was the appell.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And how do you call it?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Appell.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Appell.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I did-- had to be there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I gave a list, already, when I working, that so many are in the-- in the hospital, in the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that when they counted that they knew, five, six, eight, whatever, are missing, are with me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was standing there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was dressed, and they were all shivering.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was cold and hungry.",
      "word_count": 5
